        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were a appointed a Paladin to the brutal Judge Inquistor Einar One Eye in 1999 and only a few years into his service, and while delivering a message to Regent Galbraith in Mexico City, the betrayal of the Black Hand was revealed.  Fighting broke out on the streets between loyal Sabbat and the traitors of the so called TalMaHeRa - the death cult that had taken control of the Black Hand.  The mysterious death of Regent Galbraith only furhter inflamed the fighting and threatened to destroy the sect, only the sudden appeanrance of Temoch the Jackal in Mexico City held the sect together.  While you were busy hunting down traitors in Mexico, he claimed the throne of Caine and supposedly reformed the Black Hand.   You are glad that Temoh saved the Sword of Caine, but he should have let the Black Hand die.  Now you hear rumors that Temoch intends to allow the Hand to grow strong again and that he secretly supports the creation of a Black Hand stronghold in San Diego.  This must not come to pass.  The Sabbat will not survive another betrayal by the Black Hand."
